name: $TERRA
description:
$TERRA is distributed to the collectors of @rodellwarner's TERRARIA ⚘ series

$TERRA holders are free to gift, sell, burn, or otherwise distribute $TERRA as they wish

$TERRA will never be listed for sale by @rodellwarner

The list of holders of $TERRA constitutes the population of the TERRARIA ⚘ Community and will function as the registry for airdrops related to TERRARIA ⚘

$TERRA could have additional future utility, and could possibly be used as a form of TERRARIA ⚘ Community currency, though it is primarily conceived of as a social token for, and as a gift to, the collectors of TERRARIA ⚘

⚘⚘⚘
